bagaimana perasaan awak.

841
00:51:27,762 --> 00:51:29,762
Saya banyak buat awak menderita.

842
00:51:30,215 --> 00:51:31,715
Saya minta maaf.

843
00:51:35,970 --> 00:51:37,370
Dan...

844
00:51:38,296 --> 00:51:40,796
